00:57:09.909 --> 00:57:15.909
For decades, thousands of convicts were sentenced to forced labor

00:57:15.909 --> 00:57:20.909
in places like Royal Island, Devils Island, and Kuru.

00:57:20.909 --> 00:57:24.909
Happily, those things are in the past.

00:57:24.909 --> 00:57:29.909
Today, French Guyana remains part of the French Republic

00:57:29.909 --> 00:57:33.909
though it's more than 4,000 miles from France.

00:57:33.909 --> 00:57:40.909
